data.description: This 3 beds 1.5 baths exceptional townhome offering stylish living space. Step inside to find an inviting floor plan, and with little TLC, this property will be a great place for both relaxation and entertaining. Located in a convenient and sought-after neighborhood, this home is within close proximity to shopping, dining, and entertainment options.  Whether you're a seasoned investor or a first-time buyer looking to generate rental income, this property offers a possible great rental potential. Take advantage of the flexibility to rent out the property and capitalize on the high demand for rentals in the area. McAlpine Creek Park is just a mile away offering beautiful bike trails, walking paths and a dog park. Rental comps in the immediate area suggest this would be a great cash flowing asset for an investor. Future Silver Line light rail station has been proposed for intersection of Monroe/Village Lake Drive, just a short walk from the property. HOA covers water and sewer!
